    <briefdescription>
<para>Bluetooth OBEX TLV triplet. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Description of different data types that can be encoded into TLV triplet. Used to form arrays that are passed to the <ref refid="group__bt__obex_1gaeacfe7cb654bf33e7b387358a19fd3d3" kindref="member">bt_obex_add_header_app_param()</ref>, <ref refid="group__bt__obex_1gacfc897d66e8c14629fa4d94f3782c741" kindref="member">bt_obex_add_header_auth_challenge()</ref>, and <ref refid="group__bt__obex_1ga5433561f0e9bad6da2d94dccca1578de" kindref="member">bt_obex_add_header_auth_rsp()</ref> function. </para>
